description:
Reentrancy in Dungeon.dodgeTraps() (src/Dungeon.sol#251-260):
	External calls:
	- _attempt($traps >= 0,250 * $traps,msg.sender,Doge!,You failed.) (src/Dungeon.sol#257)
		- this.transfer(to,value) (src/Dungeon.sol#274)
		- this._burn(address(this),value) (src/Dungeon.sol#277)
	- _muhahaha() (src/Dungeon.sol#258)
		- msg.sender.call{value: 0}() (src/Dungeon.sol#290)
	External calls sending eth:
	- _muhahaha() (src/Dungeon.sol#258)
		- msg.sender.call{value: 0}() (src/Dungeon.sol#290)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- $traps -- (src/Dungeon.sol#259)
	Dungeon.$traps (src/Dungeon.sol#24) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- Dungeon.constructor() (src/Dungeon.sol#87-99)
	- Dungeon.dodgeTraps() (src/Dungeon.sol#251-260)
	- Dungeon.findMoreTraps() (src/Dungeon.sol#148-159)
	- Dungeon.removeWeb2(uint256) (src/Dungeon.sol#119-129)
markdown:
Reentrancy in [Dungeon.dodgeTraps()](src/Dungeon.sol#L251-L260):
	External calls:
	- [_attempt($traps >= 0,250 * $traps,msg.sender,Doge!,You failed.)](src/Dungeon.sol#L257)
		- [this.transfer(to,value)](src/Dungeon.sol#L274)
		- [this._burn(address(this),value)](src/Dungeon.sol#L277)
	- [_muhahaha()](src/Dungeon.sol#L258)
		- [msg.sender.call{value: 0}()](src/Dungeon.sol#L290)
	External calls sending eth:
	- [_muhahaha()](src/Dungeon.sol#L258)
		- [msg.sender.call{value: 0}()](src/Dungeon.sol#L290)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- [$traps --](src/Dungeon.sol#L259)
	[Dungeon.$traps](src/Dungeon.sol#L24) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- [Dungeon.constructor()](src/Dungeon.sol#L87-L99)
	- [Dungeon.dodgeTraps()](src/Dungeon.sol#L251-L260)
	- [Dungeon.findMoreTraps()](src/Dungeon.sol#L148-L159)
	- [Dungeon.removeWeb2(uint256)](src/Dungeon.sol#L119-L129)
